@startuml C2_container
title C2: Container Diagram - DSPy Prompt Optimizer

rectangle "User" as user
rectangle "Admin" as admin

rectangle "Web API\n(FastAPI)" as api
rectangle "Application Service\n(AgentOrchestrator)" as app_svc
rectangle "Agent Workers\n(Agent Pool)" as agents

database "Redis Cache" as redis
database "PostgreSQL\n(agents DB)" as postgres
database "DSPy Engine\n(Prompt Optimization)" as dspy

user --> api : HTTP/REST
admin --> api : Мониторинг

api --> app_svc : Вызовы
app_svc --> redis : Кэширование\nсессий
app_svc --> postgres : Персистентность
app_svc --> agents : Распределение
agents --> dspy : Оптимизация
agents --> redis : Чтение/запись
agents --> postgres : Чтение/запись

note bottom of redis
  TTL: 7 дней
  Fast read/write
end note

note bottom of postgres
  Таблицы:
  - agent_sessions
  - agent_messages
  - agent_states
  - agent_context
end note

note right of dspy
  Mipro Teleprompter
  Metric-based opt.
end note

@enduml